Comment: 10,0:07:14.58,0:07:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have proved to be an admirable son.\NEarl Hanbridge's expectations for you were well met. {it's actually Hanbridge-dono, as a weird sort of respect. they don't say hakushaku. I'm using Earl for consistency}{## they're social equals, that's why; maybe "heir" for son?}
Comment: 10,0:07:14.58,0:07:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a respectable son. Earl Hanbridge's\Nexpectations for you were well earned. {it's actually Hanbridge-dono, as a weird sort of respect. they don't say hakushaku. I'm using Earl for consistency}
Comment: 10,0:07:20.52,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,One day you will surely follow his footsteps and become a great politician.
Comment: 10,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well don't you have quite the sour look on your face, Andrew.
