Comment: 10,0:10:12.46,0:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My thoughts must have been in disarray. Ever since the moment I first laid eyes on you...
Comment: 10,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You had nestled yourself a place in my heart.
Comment: 10,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me be with you.
Comment: 10,0:10:40.71,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who said we should try it on someone.
