Comment: 10,0:11:54.27,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's {\i1}nothing{\i0} better than toying with you, Akko.
Comment: 10,0:11:54.27,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, toying with you is the best.
Comment: 10,0:12:13.68,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I must find my outlet for this restlessness in my chest.
