Comment: 10,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Witches are unnecessary.
Comment: 10,0:14:15.93,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what politics does. You have a bad habit of getting engrossed in trivialities.
Comment: 10,0:14:15.93,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's politics. You have a bad habit of getting engrossed in unnecessary things.
