Comment: 10,0:14:26.37,0:14:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't touched a piano in ten years, as you instructed.
Comment: 10,0:14:31.51,0:14:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural. You are to become the man who leads this country.
Comment: 10,0:14:37.11,0:14:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no need for effeminate music.
