Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.68,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Us"?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.59,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're going! And that includes you two.{## TLC? doesn't feel quite right}{yeah, that was too redundant}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.52,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want magic dresses...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.48,0:04:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I've got is way out of reach for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you change that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.76,0:04:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then how about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A Cinderella set?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.22,0:04:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This was our bestseller a century ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.06,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"With a wave of your wand and the magic words, \Nyou, too, can become Cinderella." {alt. "Just a wave of your stick", that's from the actual disney song}{## this is fine, goes better with the "and the magic words" part}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.89,0:04:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy now and I'll throw in a Snow White set, \Nand even knock the whole shebang down to half price! {when he goes off like that, I don't feel like there's time for two sentences}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you've got a deal!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bubide! {it's not the same as the real one}{## i think the point is that sucy is the only one getting it right, so we're free to stick close to the script here}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bubbi-babbi?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is supposed to be our carriage?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It says here the magic will run out in two hours.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.96,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. No wonder he was sitting on that shelfwarmer.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.74,0:05:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord and Lady Rodester. We have\Nbeen eagerly awaiting your arrival. {spelling}{## rodester is probably out best shot. "his excellency" doesn't work with british peerage. since they don't have a driver, i decided they're meager barons; kakka is generic enough for that}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, that's it! Earl Hanbridge's manor!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.28,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we'll be able to get in there...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.06,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Metamorphie Faciesse!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.63,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've stepped into a world straight out of a girl's fantasies.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.92,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being present as we honor my son, Andrew.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrew...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.49,0:07:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a magnificent feat, Lord Andrew. Not just anybody can be the top student at Appleton Academy. {wanted to use valedictorian but there's nothing about him graduating. also it just says appleton school, I used academy since it sounds fancy}{## valedictorian is also chiefly US use; anyway, the viscount of appleton receiving top honors at the appleton academy smells like collusion}{for the record, that was potentially a nickname}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes three consecutive years. {although this sort of implies he is at the end of his final year? not enough information}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.58,0:07:20.52,Default,,10,10,0,,You have proved to be an admirable heir. \NEarl Hanbridge's expectations for you were well placed. {it's actually Hanbridge-dono, as a weird sort of respect. they don't say hakushaku. I'm using Earl for consistency}{## they're social equals, that's why; maybe "heir" for son?}{you damn BE user, it's 'proven' in common AE. also I almost missed that mistake}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.52,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, you will surely follow his footsteps\Nand become a formidable statesman.{## hanbridge is a minister after all}{accursed politik, we hold a revolutionary war and still you dog us}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish for nothing more.{or should he say less, and be condescending?}{## nah}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.68,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like you're having\Nthe most pleasant day, Andrew.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in wasting time with formalities.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.90,0:07:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me? I'm Frank.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrew's schoolmate, I believe.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.37,0:07:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You become more beautiful each time I see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your studies appear to be progressing well.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.37,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel privileged that you would take precious time out\Nof your so-called magic education to visit me, Diana.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.55,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana and Andrew are so picturesque together. {suck my dick kinmoza haters. nobody will understand this note}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.00,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both nobles. We live in different worlds.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.38,0:08:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right! They go perfectly together with their nasty personalities.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.13,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What a surprise to see you here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is possibly going through your mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.59,0:08:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the worst!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.91,0:08:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't recall inviting you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.41,0:08:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, because you didn't!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I even be considered?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fact is that I'm already here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.33,0:08:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me a full-fledged guest of yours!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the sort of twisted logic I would expect from a witch.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Regrettably, I must ask that you leave.{tch}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to throw me out?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.17,0:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Witches, outdated and phony as they are, have no place here. {bogus sounds like a hippy, although some will argue phony sounds too much like holden}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.48,0:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even welcome a single cute and charming witch into your home?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.28,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}S-Sucy?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.87,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrew, can you really call yourself a noble\Nwith that intolerant attitude of yours?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.28,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be, Andrew. What could be a more pleasant surprise than a visit from these witches?{## let it bee}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I hate surprises.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrew?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.52,0:09:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.75,0:09:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,75)}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(75,0)}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrew?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.80,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There must have been something wrong with me. Why would I ever send you home?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.84,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.46,0:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My thoughts have been in disarray. \NEver since the moment I first laid eyes on you...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been occupying a place in my heart.{## regardless of the phrasing, it needs to be present perfect}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me be with you! {at least respond to my reference...}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Forevermore.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You used the lovelove bee?!{## reminder, plus if anything it should be the fallin lovelove bee; man i like the sound of be-in-love-bee though}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.71,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}you're{\i0} the one who said we should try it on someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.90,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait up!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.03,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrew's fallen head over heels.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a first.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Come back!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.59,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetest young lady!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How may we refer to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm Lotte Jansson.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte Jansson!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.66,0:11:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't think I'm a particularly interesting person.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hobbies are?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you betrothed?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your hand!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.07,0:11:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Lotte!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana, I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have this dance, Akko?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.16,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You must be joking.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.93,0:11:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Profess your love, with lips so fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.84,0:11:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lit my fire, you must be mine. {e-hen!}{## whew already had an edit in place for fine > tender}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sucy, do something about this!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.27,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing in the world better than toying with you, Akko.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait, Akko!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.36,0:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
