Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.68,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I must find relief from this pounding in my chest.{pretty sure it's 'for', medically speaking}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.31,0:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.71,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not enjoy it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time you've ever been desired.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, it is the first time!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.99,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's likely the last as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.98,0:12:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,True, I'll probably never—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not the issue here!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only got another hour until the Cinderella set's magic wears off!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.13,0:12:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you squish the lovelove bee with this,\Nyou can probably break its spell.{## reminder, fallin lovelove bee or be-in-love-bee}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.02,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've just gotta squish it with this!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a lovelove bee.{## reminder}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a bee? A weird-looking one.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.73,0:13:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.33,0:13:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.87,0:13:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have ever been so cold to you up until now?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.41,0:13:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I... love you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, look what you've made me say!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.71,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Andrew.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you opened our gates\Nto witches of Luna Nova.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.40,0:14:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you aware of my antipathy towards witches?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Witches and magic are the evil relics of a bygone era.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.93,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We statesmen must be the ones to consolidate power for our nation.{## i don't think this line makes a lot of sense here, so please TLC; consider "statesmen" anyway, this is a lot about leadership; is this about politicians intending to consolidate their powerbase within the nation and pushing the possible threat of witches to the side?}{no, I'm pretty sure I'm accurate here, you misinterpreted. politicians must be in charge of making the state strong, not witches. it's like whoever's on the board/cabinet}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Witches are without use.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.07,0:14:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying we must abandon their dying breed? {he even uses the word for minority}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.93,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's politics. You have a bad habit of getting engrossed in useless things. {first, I have this general feeling that 'that's politics' is right here. it's not that politics "does" make them go away, but that going away is indirectly caused? hard to explain. second, this must match his previous statement}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.42,0:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall you wishing to play the piano as a child.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.37,0:14:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I... haven't touched a piano in ten years, as you instructed.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.51,0:14:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, as a matter of course. You are to become a leader of this country.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.11,0:14:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no need for effeminate music-making.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Remove the witches. Are we clear?{colloquial etc etc}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.17,0:14:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna remove this witch here?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.09,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you threw piano out from your life.{you can have the first one, but not the second. also this could be interpreted as a physical piano}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.25,0:15:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you were so spineless. You're nothing but your father's puppet.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.68,0:15:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I highly respect my father.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.53,0:15:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He is an outstanding Minister of State\Nas well as head of our family.{## reminds me how i used this wrong in ep6; there's more than just one minister of state}{I trusted you! You were the chosen one!}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.11,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a duty to succeed my father as a statesman.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.27,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, a duty? Don't you have any dreams?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream you found on your own.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't possibly understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.38,0:15:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those chosen by fate who must\Nbear the duty of a proud lineage.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.38,0:15:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no noble, and I'm not rich either!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.30,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a brilliant witch!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the next Shiny Chariot!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.52,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I may just be a little witch right now, but I have fun every day chasing my dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.15,0:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just imagining Chariot's smile is enough\Nto fill my whole world with rainbows!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.42,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like a certain someone would understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the smirk? Are you looking down on me?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.46,0:16:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You are truly bewitching.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.75,0:16:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not how you really feel. It's just because you were stung by that magic bee.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.35,0:16:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.05,0:16:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me out! If I can squash that bee,\Nyou'll come back to your senses!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.56,0:16:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get back here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.27,0:16:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.11,0:17:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She appears to be a witch of Luna Nova.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Luna Nova witch.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.73,0:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I demand you leave the premises immediately.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.55,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, an incident has occurred.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.74,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, Miss Kagari is attempting to eliminate a dangerous bee.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A bee?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How horrid.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Andrew?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Play along. {lit. keep going}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.17,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy this as she eliminates the bee.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.51,0:17:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Flight of the Bumblebee.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.14,0:18:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you gone, Akko?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this ruckus?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Sto—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.65,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold still, Earl!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.78,0:19:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!{## should be correct, coming from a servant}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.04,0:19:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Andrew! I didn't expect you to be a pro at piano.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am. I'm perfect. {BITCH, please}{## not liking "natural" for touzen here, as you might have noticed}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike someone as slovenly as yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess the spell wore off.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.92,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.01,0:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here. There are\Nno good girls around anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I should've known. Of course this would happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.28,0:20:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.05,0:20:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I think those clothes suit you a lot better. {my fucking man}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.31,0:20:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Frank. When's the next time you have off?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to visit the library?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.18,0:20:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is there anywhere else you'd like to go?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you mean together?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.57,0:20:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the feeling we'd get along well.{## cute pairing}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.71,0:20:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it possible to be so beautiful?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's return home.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.73,0:20:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte Jansson.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.68,0:20:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's homely at first glance.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.62,0:21:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I saw her sad smile, and I realized...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the sort of kindhearted girl\Nyou rarely find nowadays. {if only there were multiple, but alas}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.41,0:21:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you and Atsuko Kagari?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.46,0:21:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.74,0:21:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, you didn't kick her out.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.52,0:21:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You ignored an order from your witch-hating father.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is a brilliant statesman.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.19,0:21:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that does not mean our opinions will always align.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.05,0:21:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.09,0:21:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl has caught your interest.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.56,0:21:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.29,0:21:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Lotte! Frank asked you out, but you refused?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.95,0:21:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm happy he did, but I felt it'd be rude to go on a date with him before I developed any feelings.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.14,0:21:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him we should start as friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.09,0:21:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, I bet you think you don't need a \Nboyfriend as long as you have {\i1}night fall{\i0}. {/s/boyfriend/girlfriend s/nightfall/anime}{## yeah...}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.87,0:21:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true. So Akko, how about you? {how do we manage to miss each other on these so often}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.01,0:22:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it make you happy to have a prince put the moves on you?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.23,0:22:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was only because the bee stung him!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.62,0:22:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it put you on cloud nine.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.40,0:22:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Profess your love, with lips so fine.\NYou've lit my fire, you must be mine."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.32,0:22:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There might come a day when Andrew says "I love you" for real.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.89,0:22:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! That selfish, conceited guy would never say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.21,0:22:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'd tell him?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.73,0:22:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no! Never, ever!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.60,0:22:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously never! Even if I died!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.38,0:22:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
